<h2>üí° Quick Reference Cheat Sheet</h2>

<h3>HTML Basics</h3>
<pre>&lt;!-- Comment: explains code to humans --&gt;
&lt;tag&gt;Content&lt;/tag&gt;              &lt;!-- Most tags need opening & closing --&gt;
&lt;tag attribute="value"&gt;         &lt;!-- Attributes change tag behavior --&gt;
